</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#D5D4D5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/udarkomen42.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DarkOmen42</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Boardaholic</span><br> <font color=#000033>(2/7/02 9:45:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumrantsandravesbalancingissues.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1644.topic&index=46>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .</span><hr size=1> I drive the speed I can reasonable handle depending what road I'm on and how well I know it.<br>
